Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这些孩子不用费心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,会进行光合成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,光合成？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 怎么了？ 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没什么事 过得还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,伊扎那有段时间没回家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没听到你的声音了 想听听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我要走了 对不起了 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,下次休息我会回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的电话是奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 最近工作好像很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才特意没有回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是做什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谷风长道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真亏你把她 不 把那个带回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,驾驶员训练生科户濑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,长道一个人让人担心所以就跟着一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,外生研 田宽笯美 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在本体被破坏前分离的胞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在本体被破坏后还能继续存活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,寿命有多长还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,奇居子复制这么完整的人类是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,长道为什么被叫来啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是测试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:04:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,测试？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那个有没有人类的知性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是为什么是长道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那个叫着谷风驾驶员的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 长道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 让光线通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,星…白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,星白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,长道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:47.66,fat,,0,0,0,,{\frz349.1\fs40\pos(226.045,88.801)\be2\c&H434343&}葱鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这么消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那个不一定是攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,长道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 这不是谷风吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,弦打
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 你们确实是
